*Vam* je danas divan dan (You have a wonderful day today).

*Vama* je današnji dan bio uspešan (Your day was successful).

*Vamo* da vidimo šta se dešava (Let's go see what's happening).

*Vama* je potrebno da dobijete podršku (You need support).

*Vame* je potrebno mnogo više sna (We need much more sleep).

*Vamo* da odemo na ručak (Let's go out for lunch).